name: Lu 20 Tuner
details:
Led-type TunerFeatures/Specifications:
Durable die-cast housing
LED display with 3-color indicator for maximum visibility
Able to 5 half step (bbbbb) flat/down tuning
Further Specs:
Tuning Range: C1( 32.70Hz) - B5 (987.77Hz)
Calibration: 436Hz - 445Hz
Power Supply: 9V 006P x 1 or AC ADAPTER Ibanez AC109
Input: Input Jack, DC Jack
Output: Output Jack, Dry Out Jack
